  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK365">
<l>aṟṟava reṉpā ravāvaṟṟār maṟṟaiyā</l>
<l>raṟṟāka vaṟṟa tilar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They are said to be free (from future birth) who are freed from desire; all others (who, whatever else they may be free from, are not freed from desire) are not thus free.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
